cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS 

This paper proposes a gradient-based approach for locally adjusting hyperparameters during training of the model. The approach is tested on image classification tasks (MNIST, SVHN, CIFAR-10), which suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
